Package: QCmemo
Type: Package
Title: PSE QC Memo Helper Functions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Colin", "Hill", email = "colin.hill@mdrc.org",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Colin Hill <colin.hill@mdrc.org>
Description: This package loads required libraries and custom functions to
    help the user generate a QC memo in RMarkdown. This package was designed to 
    be used with the QC Memo template, but the functions may be useful in other
    settings as well. 
